 To all my friends good luck and happy hunting. Some are wondering if i will come back? Even if i wanted to some officers will take offense of this post and probbly not want me back even if i change my mind. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bhordeofshadows15583.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rorek>Rorek</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Shadow Scribe</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#8B0000>(2/9/02 3:07:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=119.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: WHY I DEGUILDED</span><hr size=1> Well, Ill be the first to reply with simply, Good Luck to yas Tank. Also, I believe it was mentioned once before somewhere, It is very difficult to seriously offend someone from Horde, we are all easy going people who love to have fun and for someone to resent you for anything would be wrong. Im sure if you ever decided to come back you would be welcomed with open arms, unless of course i am mistaken and you really did do something bad and unforgiveable. But take all the time you need Im sure you will be dearly missed.<br>
<br>
